15/*! \file */
16
17#include <config.h>
18
19#include <string.h>
20
21#include <isc/buffer.h>
22#include <isc/region.h>
23#include <isc/md.h>
24#include <isc/util.h>
25
26#include <dns/ds.h>
27#include <dns/fixedname.h>
28#include <dns/name.h>
29#include <dns/rdata.h>
30#include <dns/rdatastruct.h>
31#include <dns/result.h>
32
33#include <dst/dst.h>
34
35isc_result_t
36dns_ds_buildrdata(dns_name_t *owner, dns_rdata_t *key,
37 dns_dsdigest_t digest_type, unsigned char *buffer,
38 dns_rdata_t *rdata)
39{
40 dns_fixedname_t fname;
41 dns_name_t *name;
42 unsigned char digest[ISC_MAX_MD_SIZE];
43 unsigned int digestlen;
44 isc_region_t r;
45 isc_buffer_t b;
46 dns_rdata_ds_t ds;
47 isc_md_t *md;
48 isc_md_type_t md_type = 0;
49 isc_result_t ret;
50
51 REQUIRE(key != NULL);
52 REQUIRE(key->type == dns_rdatatype_dnskey ||
53 key->type == dns_rdatatype_cdnskey);
54
55 if (!dst_ds_digest_supported(digest_type)) {
56 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
57 }
58
59 switch (digest_type) {
60 case DNS_DSDIGEST_SHA1:
61 md_type = ISC_MD_SHA1;
62 break;
63
64 case DNS_DSDIGEST_SHA384:
65 md_type = ISC_MD_SHA384;
66 break;
67
68 case DNS_DSDIGEST_SHA256:
69 md_type = ISC_MD_SHA256;
70 break;
71
72 default:
73 INSIST(0);
74 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
75 }
76
77 name = dns_fixedname_initname(&fname);
78 (void)dns_name_downcase(owner, name, NULL);
79
80 memset(buffer, 0, DNS_DS_BUFFERSIZE);
81 isc_buffer_init(&b, buffer, DNS_DS_BUFFERSIZE);
82
83 md = isc_md_new();
84 if (md == NULL) {
85 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
86 }
87
88 ret = isc_md_init(md, md_type);
89 if (ret != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
90 goto end;
91 }
92
93 dns_name_toregion(name, &r);
94
95 ret = isc_md_update(md, r.base, r.length);
96 if (ret != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
97 goto end;
98 }
99
100 dns_rdata_toregion(key, &r);
101 INSIST(r.length >= 4);
102
103 ret = isc_md_update(md, r.base, r.length);
104 if (ret != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
105 goto end;
106 }
107
108 ret = isc_md_final(md, digest, &digestlen);
109 if (ret != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
110 goto end;
111 }
112
113 ds.mctx = NULL;
114 ds.common.rdclass = key->rdclass;
115 ds.common.rdtype = dns_rdatatype_ds;
116 ds.algorithm = r.base[3];
117 ds.key_tag = dst_region_computeid(&r);
118 ds.digest_type = digest_type;
119 ds.digest = digest;
120 ds.length = digestlen;
121
122 ret = dns_rdata_fromstruct(rdata, key->rdclass, dns_rdatatype_ds,
123 &ds, &b);
124end:
125 if (md != NULL) {
126 isc_md_free(md);
127 }
128 return (ret);
129}
